No problems here! This section covers phones, camcorders, digital cameras, PSP etc and tells you what memory it takes and the maximum capacity it is designed for.. a life saver! Once you've placed your order you are kept fully informed about the progress and when you can expect to receive it. If you do nothing else here, have a read of the website.. just make sure you have spare underwear as you will be wetting yourself! Long live the hens! Overall Rating
